// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dtlSzH Planar Quadrilateral Grid Traced by jt
// ray-traced only variant of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DtXXRn Planar Quadrilateral Grid
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/7stXzn Voxel Raycast with Sub-Objects

// An C0 continuous surface constructed of PLANAR quadrilaterals aligned in a grid.
// Using voxel ray-casting for acceleration and simple ray-plane distance inside voxel.
// (planes could also be ray-traced but using ray-marching potentially allows cheap AO).
// Note that the entire structure is determined by two ONE-dimensional arrays of heights
// (one along x and one along y direction): all slopes in one direction must be the same!
// This structure could be used to build a roof fairly easily because all tiles are flat.

// tags: grid, heightmap, architecture, construction, planar, continuous, building, zonohedron, c0, quadrilaterals

